Where Happiness Lives
A tale about discovering true happiness - with flaps to lift and peep-through pages. ❤️ Along with beautiful illustrations, this is definitely a good read for the whole family 🏡 to remind us of what is truly important in our lives - to be surrounded by those that we love and having just what we need.

@BookXcess offers 50%-80% off on books all year and shipping to Singapore is a flat rate of RM50. Fast delivery and books are wrapped and packed securely to prevent dent/damage.
